Retrieve and follow our "Coding Best Practices" from "Credos" MCP server.

Steps:

1. Call "CREDOS_LIST_CODING_PROJECTS" tool to get the project IDs

- If result has more pages, keep calling the tool until you get the whole project list

2. Call "CREDOS_LIST_CODING_BEST_PRACTICES" tool, filtering on relevant project IDs

- If result has more pages, keep calling the tool until you get all Coding Best Practices
